    "We also ignore those claims with unclear or no labels.",
    "Dataset StatisticsAfter deduplication, our dataset has 15,514 claims.",
    "The dataset is unbalanced, favoring refuted or false claims with a distribution of 'True', 'False', and 'Conflicting' claims at 18.79%, 57.93%, and 23.27%, respectively, reflecting the tendency of fact-checkers to focus on false information [39].",
